description: Two figures in spacesuits stand on the moon's surface, dotted with craters and featuring a conical structure in the background under a starry sky. One figure is enthusiastically declaring their arrival on the moon while punching the other figure's helmet, causing it to shatter and debris to fly around their head. This absurd act of violence immediately after achieving a monumental goal introduces dark humor and surrealism to the scene.
caption: “We’ve made it, Warren! ... The moon!”
